{{Lowercase}}
''' cD型星系'''<ref>Sidereal Times, June 2002, page 3</ref><ref>Proceedings of PATRAS 2008, page 59</ref>或'''cD星系'''<ref>Galaxy Clusters, Jan Hartlap, page 3</ref>，是[[星系|星系]]型態分類中的一種類型，是巨大的[[橢圓星系|橢圓星系]]，[[D型星系|D型]]的子類型，有著[[恆星|恆星]]的巨大[[星系暈|星系暈]]<ref>Surface Photometry and the Structure of Elliptical Galaxies, [http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/level5/Sept01/Kormendy/Kormendy11.html "Chapter 11. cD and Brightest Cluster Galaxies"] {{Wayback|url=http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/level5/Sept01/Kormendy/Kormendy11.html |date=20080705065004 }}, '''John Kormendy, S. Djorgovski''', ''1989''</ref>。它們可以在一些富[[星系團|星系團]]接近中心的地區被發現<ref>A Dictionary of Astronomy, [http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1O80-cDgalaxy.html "cD galaxy"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1O80-cDgalaxy.html |date=20200312083919 }} (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref>，它們也被稱為'''超巨橢圓星系'''<ref>encyclopedia.com [http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1O80-supergiantelliptical.html "supergiant elliptical"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1O80-supergiantelliptical.html |date=20200111021425 }}</ref>或'''中心主導星系'''<ref name=UoCoGd/>。

==cD星系==
cD-型是在[[星系分類#耶基斯（或摩根）分類|耶基斯星系分類]]中的一種類型，耶基斯星類中的一兩個類型依然被普遍的使用，包括D類型<ref>An Atlas of DRAGNs, [http://www.jb.man.ac.uk/atlas/gloss.html#cD "Glossary"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jb.man.ac.uk/atlas/gloss.html#cD |date=20120402205435 }}, '''J. P. Leahy''', ''15 March 1997'' (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref>。在"cD"中的"c"是指這些種星系都很大，因此是''巨大星系''，而"D"指的是這些星系的外觀是瀰漫性的事實<ref>Global Telescope Network, [http://gtn.sonoma.edu/resources/normal_galaxies/types.php "Types of Galaxies"] {{Wayback|url=http://gtn.sonoma.edu/resources/normal_galaxies/types.php |date=20100716001648 }}, '''Kevin McLin''', ''14 April 2010'' (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref>。 A backformation of "cD"背後的訊息通常意味著是''中心主導星系'' (''central Dominant galaxy'')<ref name=UoCoGd>"Uncertainties on Clusters of Galaxies Distances", '''C. Adami, M.P. Ulmer''', ''18 July 2000'', {{arxiv|astro-ph/0007265}} (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref>。 cD也經常被認為視周遭最大的星系<ref>Universe Today, [http://www.universetoday.com/guide-to-space/galaxies/what-is-the-largest-galaxy/ "What is the Largest Galaxy?"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.universetoday.com/guide-to-space/galaxies/what-is-the-largest-galaxy/ |date=20100430182701 }}, '''Fraser Cain''' (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref><ref>EurekAlert, [http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2005-01/ou-sol010505.php "Scientists observe largest explosion in space"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2005-01/ou-sol010505.php |date=20171107060122 }}, '''Andrea Gibson''', ''5 January 2005'' (accessed 15 April 2010)</ref>。

cD星系與[[透鏡星系|透鏡星系]] (S0) 或[[橢圓星系|橢圓星系]] (E#) 相似，但是大了許多倍，有一些的半徑發展已經超過百萬[[光年|光年]]<ref>Encyclopædia Britannica, [http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/100915/cD-galaxy "cD-galaxy"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/100915/cD-galaxy |date=20110607054850 }} (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref>。他們呈現類似橢圓的形狀，與巨大的低表面光度外層<ref name="ICyese-cD"/>。目前，我們認為cD是[[星系合併|星系合併]]的結果<ref name="cosmos-sao-CDgalaxies">COSMOS - The SAO Encyclopedia of Astronomy, [http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/cosmos/C/CD+Galaxies "CD Galaxies"] {{Wayback|url=http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/cosmos/C/CD+Galaxies |date=20120321152801 }}, '''Swinburne University of Technology''' (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref>。有些cD有多個[[星系#活躍星系|星系核]] <ref>Internet Encyclopedia of Science, [http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/D/D_galaxy.html "D galaxy"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/D/D_galaxy.html |date=20171025075026 }}, '''David Darling''' (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref>。cD星系經常是在[[最亮團星系|最亮團星系]] (brightest cluster galaxy，BCG) 中的一種星系<ref>IAU Symposium 245, "Star Formation in Bulges from GALEX", '''Sukyoung K. Yi''', ''5 September 2007'', {{doi|10.1017/S174392130801819X}}, {{arxiv|0709.0177}} (accessed 14 April 2010)</ref>。許多[[化石星系群|化石星系群]]星系也類似於cD BCG星系，讓一些理論學家推測cD星系是化石星系群發展的結果，然後新的星系團再累積在化石星系群的周圍<ref>Universe Today, [http://www.universetoday.com/2006/04/27/how-do-fossil-galaxy-clusters-form-so-quickly/ "How Do Fossil Galaxy Clusters Form so Quickly?"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.universetoday.com/2006/04/27/how-do-fossil-galaxy-clusters-form-so-quickly/ |date=20071014125058 }}, '''Fraser Cain''', ''27 April 2006'' (accessed 15 April 2010)</ref>。然而，cD星系本身尚未被發現是[[視場星系|場星系]]，不同於化石星系群<ref name="ICyese-cD">Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society, "Intracluster light and the extended stellar envelopes of cD galaxies: an analytical description", '''Marc S. Seigar, Alister W. Graham, Helmut Jerjen''', ''July 2007'', Volume 378, Issue 4, pp. 1575-1588, {{doi|10.1111/j.1365-2966.2007.11899.x}}, {{bibcode|2007MNRAS.378.1575S}}, {{arxiv|astro-ph/0612229v2}} (accessed 15 April 2010)</ref> cD型星系大約有20%是最亮團星系 (BCG)<ref name="ICyese-cD"/>。

==成長==
赫柏特 J 路德在1965年率先提出cD星系是在星系團中心的螺旋星系經由星系合併形成的學說<ref>{{Cite thesis |degree=PhD |chapter= |title=The Dynamics of the Coma Cluster of Galaxies |bibcode=1965PhDT.........3R |author=Herbert J. Rood |last=Rood |first=H. J. |year=1965 |publisher=The University of Michigan }}</ref>。 在此一"[[交互作用星系#星系吞噬|吞噬]]"模式下的成長，會導致cD星系壓倒性的直徑和亮度<ref name="curious">{{Cite web|url=http://curious.astro.cornell.edu/|title=Curious About Astronomy?|accessdate=28 March 2007|archive-date=2007-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070322215236/http://curious.astro.cornell.edu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在星團中第二亮的星系通常是低亮度的，通常這是已經被"吃"的結果<ref>{{Cite journal
