===動態摩擦===
[[動態摩擦|動態摩擦]]被認為在cD星系於星系團中心形成的過程中扮演著非常重要的角色<ref name="DM1983">
{{Cite journal
  | doi = 10.1086/160571
  | last = Merritt
  | first = David
  | authorlink = David Merritt
  | title = Relaxation and tidal stripping in rich clusters of galaxies. I. Evolution of the mass distribution
  | journal = The Astrophysical Journal
  | volume = 264
  | pages = 24–48
  | date = January 1983
  | bibcode = 1983ApJ...264...24M}}</ref>。當大星系在星系團中的運動吸引了較小的星系和[[暗物質|暗物質]]進入它的尾跡時，這個過程就開始了。這些追隨在大星系後面的過密物質和穩定施加在其上的引力，導致大星系的速度減緩。當它是去[[動能|動能]]，大星系會逐漸盤旋著朝向星系團的中心。一旦如此，大星系中的[[恆星|恆星]]、[[氣體|氣體]]、[[灰塵|塵埃]]和[[暗物質|暗物質]]，以及它的尾跡中的星系，都將如同之前加入它們的星系，有著相同的命運<ref name="DM1984">
{{Cite journal
  | doi = 10.1086/161590
  | last = Merritt
  | first = David
  | authorlink = David Merritt
  | title = Relaxation and tidal stripping in rich clusters of galaxies. II. Evolution of the luminosity distribution
  | journal = The Astrophysical Journal
  | volume = 276
  | pages = 26–37
  | date = January 1984
  | bibcode = 1984ApJ...276...26M}}</ref>。經由這樣的累積，將造成巨大或超大的瀰漫或橢圓星系<ref name="DM1985">
{{Cite journal
  | doi = 10.1086/162860
  | last = Merritt
  | first = David
  | authorlink = David Merritt
  | title = Relaxation and tidal stripping in rich clusters of galaxies. III. Growth of a massive central galaxy
  | journal = The Astrophysical Journal
  | volume = 289
  | pages = 18–32
  | date = February 1985
  | bibcode = 1985ApJ...289...18M}}</ref>。合併的中心或合併星系殘骸在很長的時間中都能被辨認，始cD星系會呈現多"核"的狀態<ref>{{Cite journal
  | doi = 10.1086/184257
